Introduction

Seowon is a singer, musical actress, and TV show host under Lean Branding. In 2023, Seowon participated in the SBS survival show "Universe Ticket" where she finished 5th place, securing her spot as a member of the South Korean project girl group UNIS.

Seowon debuted as a member of UNIS on March 27, 2024, with their first mini-album "WE UNIS" and the title track "SUPERWOMAN."

On April 24, 2021, she made her debut solo with the digital single, “Shoulder Dance”
